

BABA

   There are at least two different meanings for this Tagalog word in
   standard dictionaries.
   babà
   chin

   Sa anatomiya, ito ay bahagi ng katawan na nasa ibaba ng bibig. In
   anatomy, this is the part of the body that’s below the mouth.
