   kapandakan, ikli, igsi; lunsad, lusong, pagpanaog; puti, itas, ani
   baba
   lowness

   baba
   to descend

   Baba na kayo.
   You guys come down already.

   Bababa ka ba?
   Are you going down? (elevator)

   Bababa ka ba?
   Are you getting off? (vehicle)

   Bababa ba ang elebeytor?
   Will the elevator be going down?

   Bakit mo ako binabaan sa telepono?
   Why did you hang up on me on the phone?
   “Why did you put down the phone?”
